{% doc %}
  @description Amount-based multi-milestone cart progress bar. Renders a
    helper-text message line, a horizontal track with evenly spaced milestone
    markers (independent inactive/active states), and an animated fill driven
    by the live cart total. All campaign data (bar styling, exclusions,
    milestones) comes from the portal-managed spectrum_progress_campaign
    metaobject's `config` json envelope; only presentation knobs remain as
    snippet props.

  @param c {object} Variant content object injected by the snippet wrapper.
    All keys optional — defaults below.
  @param c.campaign_handle {string} Handle of a spectrum_progress_campaign
    metaobject. Empty = first active campaign carrying a config envelope.
  @param c.bar_height {number} Track height in px.
  @param c.show_labels {boolean} Show milestone labels.
  @param c.message_alignment {string} 'left' | 'center' | 'right'
  @param c.fill_animation {boolean} Animate fill width changes.
{% enddoc %}

{% comment %}
  Data contract: the campaign envelope (ProgressBarEnvelope v2 in
  @spectrum/core/types/progress-bar) is read HERE in Liquid because
  metaobjects are not available to cart.js. Thresholds arrive as integer
  cents; the asset JS only does cart math + DOM state updates on cart
  events. SSR and the runtime must stay in lockstep — both compute the
  eligible total (sum of final_line_price excluding envelope-listed product
  ids), the same fill interpolation, and the same helper-text messaging:
  the next unreached milestone's inactive helperText (with {remaining}
  money token) until all milestones are reached, then the final milestone's
  active helperText.

  Campaign selection skips active entries without a config envelope so
  legacy hand-seeded metaobjects can coexist during migration without
  blanking the bar.

  Node positions are evenly spaced at index/(count+1) — the track extends
  past the last marker (reference design) and stays stable however uneven
  the threshold amounts are. Fill interpolates linearly between node
  positions.

  Color pattern: theme tokens with the reference design's palette as
  fallbacks (light-blue card #e7f0fc, royal-blue fill #4b79dd, rest-track
  #c9daf3, deep-blue strong text #2f55a4).
{% endcomment %}

{% stylesheet %}
.sai-vg4guong {
  display: block;
  /* Positioning context + clip for the ribbon-rain celebration pieces. */
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: var(--sai-color-info-bg, #e7f0fc);
  border-radius: var(--sai-radius-card, 12px);
  padding: var(--sai-space-5, 1.4rem) var(--sai-space-4, 1rem) var(--sai-space-3, 0.75rem);
}
.sai-vg4guong__message {
  margin: 0 0 var(--sai-space-2, 0.5rem);
  font-family: var(--sai-font-heading, inherit);
  font-size: var(--sai-font-size-lg, 1.25rem);
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.35;
  color: var(--sai-color-info-text, #647eb5);
}
.sai-vg4guong__message strong { color: var(--sai-color-info-strong, #2f55a4); font-weight: 700; }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-align="center"] .sai-vg4guong__message { text-align: center; }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-align="right"] .sai-vg4guong__message { text-align: right; }
.sai-vg4guong__submsg {
  margin: var(--sai-space-2, 0.5rem) 0 0;
  font-size: var(--sai-font-size-sm, 0.875rem);
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.35;
  color: var(--sai-color-info-text, #647eb5);
}
.sai-vg4guong__submsg:empty { display: none; }
.sai-vg4guong__submsg strong { color: var(--sai-color-info-strong, #2f55a4); font-weight: 700; }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-align="center"] .sai-vg4guong__submsg { text-align: center; }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-align="right"] .sai-vg4guong__submsg { text-align: right; }

.sai-vg4guong__bar { position: relative; padding: 16px 0; }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-labels="on"] .sai-vg4guong__bar { margin-bottom: 3.1em; }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-labels="on"][data-sai-has-above="on"] .sai-vg4guong__bar { margin-top: 3.1em; }
.sai-vg4guong__track {
  position: absolute; left: 0; right: 0; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
  height: var(--sai-vg4guong-bar-h, 5px);
  background: var(--sai-color-track, #c9daf3);
  border-radius: 999px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-corner="square"] .sai-vg4guong__track { border-radius: 0; }
/* Stepper bar: the track renders as equal segments with gaps at each
   marker interval (interval width set inline via --sai-vg4guong-seg). */
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-style="stepper"] .sai-vg4guong__track {
  -webkit-mask: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #000 0 calc(var(--sai-vg4guong-seg, 25%) - 6px), transparent calc(var(--sai-vg4guong-seg, 25%) - 6px) var(--sai-vg4guong-seg, 25%));
  mask: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #000 0 calc(var(--sai-vg4guong-seg, 25%) - 6px), transparent calc(var(--sai-vg4guong-seg, 25%) - 6px) var(--sai-vg4guong-seg, 25%));
}
.sai-vg4guong__fill {
  height: 100%; width: 0;
  background: var(--sai-color-accent, #4b79dd);
  border-radius: inherit;
}
/* Candy-stripe at 45° — white at 50% alpha over the fill color reads as two
   alternating tones (reference: avimee cart bar, 32px tile). */
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-fill-style="striped"] .sai-vg4guong__fill {
  background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5) 25%, transparent 25%, transparent 50%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5) 50%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5) 75%, transparent 75%, transparent);
  background-size: 32px 32px;
}
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-anim="on"] .sai-vg4guong__fill { transition: width 0.45s ease; }

.sai-vg4guong__node-wrap {
  position: absolute; top: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}
/* Each marker carries both state renders; the reached class flips them in
   one frame with no DOM writes. */
.sai-vg4guong__state--active { display: none; }
.sai-vg4guong__node-wrap--reached .sai-vg4guong__state--inactive { display: none; }
.sai-vg4guong__node-wrap--reached .sai-vg4guong__state--active { display: block; }

.sai-vg4guong__node {
  position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  background: var(--sai-color-surface-raised, #ffffff);
  border: 2px solid var(--sai-color-track, #c9daf3);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--sai-color-info-bg, #e7f0fc);
  color: transparent;
}
.sai-vg4guong__state--active .sai-vg4guong__node {
  background: var(--sai-color-accent, #4b79dd);
  border-color: var(--sai-color-surface-raised, #ffffff);
  color: var(--sai-color-surface-raised, #ffffff);
}
.sai-vg4guong__node svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; display: block; }
.sai-vg4guong__node--asset { width: 40px; height: 40px; }
.sai-vg4guong__node img { width: 26px; height: 26px; display: block; object-fit: contain; }
/* A custom node image overrides the glyph (empty dot / checkmark); the accent
   fill is dropped so any image reads on a clean surface, active or not. */
.sai-vg4guong__node--img { background: var(--sai-color-surface-raised, #ffffff); }
.sai-vg4guong__state--active .sai-vg4guong__node--img {
  background: var(--sai-color-surface-raised, #ffffff);
  border-color: var(--sai-color-accent, #4b79dd);
}

/* Pin marker: circle riding above the track with a pointer tail. */
.sai-vg4guong__pin {
  position: absolute; bottom: calc(50% + 8px); left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  background: var(--sai-color-surface-raised, #ffffff);
  border: 2px solid var(--sai-color-track, #c9daf3);
  box-shadow: 0 1px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
}
.sai-vg4guong__pin::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; top: 100%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  border: 6px solid transparent;
  border-top-color: var(--sai-color-surface-raised, #ffffff);
}
.sai-vg4guong__state--active .sai-vg4guong__pin { border-color: var(--sai-color-accent, #4b79dd); }
.sai-vg4guong__pin img { width: 26px; height: 26px; display: block; object-fit: contain; }

.sai-vg4guong__label {
  position: absolute; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  top: calc(50% + 22px);
  /* Hard 110px cap: adjacent labels sit one node-gap apart, so anything
     wider than ~the gap collides at narrow widths. */
  width: 110px; max-width: 110px;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.25;
  color: var(--sai-color-text, #3a4456);
}
.sai-vg4guong__label--above { top: auto; bottom: calc(50% + 22px); }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-labels="off"] .sai-vg4guong__label { display: none; }

.sai-vg4guong__node-wrap--pulse .sai-vg4guong__state--active { animation: sai-vg4guong-pulse 0.5s ease; }
@keyframes sai-vg4guong-pulse {
  0% { transform: scale(1); }
  50% { transform: scale(1.18); }
  100% { transform: scale(1); }
}
.sai-vg4guong__confetti {
  position: absolute; width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 2px;
  pointer-events: none;
  animation: sai-vg4guong-burst 0.9s ease-out forwards;
}
@keyframes sai-vg4guong-burst {
  0% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
  100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(var(--sai-vg4guong-cx, 0), var(--sai-vg4guong-cy, -60px)) rotate(320deg); }
}
/* Ribbon-rain celebration: strips drop from the card's top edge, swaying
   sideways and tumbling. Width/height are the ribbon proportions; image
   particles override them inline. */
.sai-vg4guong__ribbon {
  position: absolute; top: -20px; width: 7px; height: 16px; border-radius: 2px;
  pointer-events: none;
  animation: sai-vg4guong-rain 1.8s ease-in forwards;
}
@keyframes sai-vg4guong-rain {
  0% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
  70% { opacity: 1; }
  100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(var(--sai-vg4guong-rx, 0), var(--sai-vg4guong-ry, 140px)) rotate(var(--sai-vg4guong-rr, 540deg)); }
}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .sai-vg4guong[data-sai-anim="on"] .sai-vg4guong__fill { transition: none; }
  .sai-vg4guong__node-wrap--pulse .sai-vg4guong__state--active { animation: none; }
  .sai-vg4guong__confetti { display: none; }
  .sai-vg4guong__ribbon { display: none; }
}
{% endstylesheet %}

{%- liquid
  assign campaign_handle = c.campaign_handle | default: ''
  assign bar_height = c.bar_height | default: 5
  assign message_alignment = c.message_alignment | default: 'center'
  if c.show_labels == nil
    assign show_labels = true
  else
    assign show_labels = c.show_labels
  endif
  if c.fill_animation == nil
    assign fill_animation = true
  else
    assign fill_animation = c.fill_animation
  endif

  assign campaign = nil
  if campaign_handle != blank
    assign campaign = shop.metaobjects['spectrum_progress_campaign'][campaign_handle]
  endif
  if campaign == nil
    for entry in shop.metaobjects['spectrum_progress_campaign'].values
      if campaign == nil and entry.active.value and entry.config.value
        assign campaign = entry
      endif
    endfor
  endif

  assign cfg = nil
  if campaign
    assign cfg = campaign.config.value
  endif
  assign milestones = nil
  if cfg
    assign milestones = cfg.milestones
  endif

  assign labels_attr = 'off'
  if show_labels
    assign labels_attr = 'on'
  endif
  assign anim_attr = 'off'
  if fill_animation
    assign anim_attr = 'on'
  endif
-%}

{%- comment -%}
  Server-rendered first paint: the eligible total, fill width, reached
  marker states, and the helper-text message are computed here from the
  cart global so a theme section morph lands fully populated. The runtime
  repaints the identical state on init, then owns all subsequent updates.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- liquid
  assign excluded_key = '|'
  if cfg
    for pid in cfg.excludedProductIds
      assign pid_s = pid | round | append: ''
      assign excluded_key = excluded_key | append: pid_s | append: '|'
    endfor
  endif

  assign cart_total = 0
  for item in cart.items
    assign item_pid = item.product_id | append: ''
    assign item_needle = '|' | append: item_pid | append: '|'
    unless excluded_key contains item_needle
      assign cart_total = cart_total | plus: item.final_line_price
    endunless
  endfor

  assign ms_count = 0
  if milestones
    assign ms_count = milestones.size
  endif
  assign ms_denom = ms_count | plus: 1
  assign seg_pct = 100.0 | divided_by: ms_denom
  assign fill_pct = 0.0
  assign reached_count = 0
  assign prev_t = 0
  assign prev_p = 0.0
  assign found_next = false
  assign next_title = ''
  assign next_helper = ''
  assign next_remaining = 0
  assign last_title = ''
  assign last_active_helper = ''
  assign reached_active_helper = ''
  assign reached_active_title = ''
  assign has_above = 'off'
  for m in milestones
    assign t_cents = m.thresholdCents | round
    assign node_p = forloop.index | times: 100.0 | divided_by: ms_denom
    if m.inactive.labelPlacement == 'above' or m.active.labelPlacement == 'above'
      assign has_above = 'on'
    endif
    if m.inactive.markerStyle == 'pin_asset_text' or m.active.markerStyle == 'pin_asset_text'
      assign has_above = 'on'
    endif
    assign last_title = m.title
    assign last_active_helper = m.active.helperText | default: ''
    if cart_total >= t_cents
      assign reached_count = reached_count | plus: 1
      assign fill_pct = node_p
      assign prev_t = t_cents
      assign prev_p = node_p
      assign m_active_helper = m.active.helperText | default: ''
      if m_active_helper != blank
        assign reached_active_helper = m_active_helper
        assign reached_active_title = m.title
      endif
    elsif found_next == false
      assign found_next = true
      assign next_title = m.title
      assign next_helper = m.inactive.helperText | default: ''
      assign next_remaining = t_cents | minus: cart_total
      assign seg_t = t_cents | minus: prev_t
      assign seg_p = node_p | minus: prev_p
      assign into_seg = cart_total | minus: prev_t
      if seg_t > 0 and into_seg > 0
        assign fill_pct = into_seg | times: 1.0 | divided_by: seg_t | times: seg_p | plus: prev_p
      endif
    endif
  endfor
  if ms_count > 0 and reached_count == ms_count
    assign fill_pct = 100.0
  endif

  if ms_count > 0 and reached_count == ms_count
    assign msg_tmpl = last_active_helper
    if msg_tmpl == blank
      assign msg_tmpl = "Congrats! You've unlocked {reward} 🎉"
    endif
    assign reward_label_ssr = last_title
    assign remaining_money = ''
  else
    assign msg_tmpl = next_helper
    if msg_tmpl == blank
      assign msg_tmpl = 'Add {remaining} more to unlock {reward}'
    endif
    assign reward_label_ssr = next_title
    assign remaining_money = next_remaining | money
  endif
  assign reward_html = '<strong>' | append: reward_label_ssr | append: '</strong>'
  assign msg_ssr = msg_tmpl | replace: '{remaining_amount}', remaining_money | replace: '{remaining}', remaining_money | replace: '{reward}', reward_html

  comment
    Sub-message below the bar: the highest reached milestone's active
    message. Suppressed once all milestones are reached — the bar-level
    message shows the final active helper then, and both saying the same
    thing reads as a bug. Empty renders collapse via the :empty CSS rule.
  endcomment
  assign submsg_ssr = ''
  if reached_count < ms_count and reached_active_helper != blank
    assign sub_reward_html = '<strong>' | append: reached_active_title | append: '</strong>'
    assign submsg_ssr = reached_active_helper | replace: '{remaining_amount}', '' | replace: '{remaining}', '' | replace: '{reward}', sub_reward_html
  endif
-%}

{%- if milestones and ms_count > 0 -%}
<div class="sai-vg4guong"
     data-sai-progress
     data-sai-style="{{ cfg.barStyle | default: 'continuous' }}"
     data-sai-corner="{{ cfg.barBorderRadius | default: 'rounded' }}"
     data-sai-fill-style="{{ cfg.fillStyle | default: 'solid' }}"
     data-sai-align="{{ message_alignment }}"
     data-sai-labels="{{ labels_attr }}"
     data-sai-has-above="{{ has_above }}"
     data-sai-anim="{{ anim_attr }}"
     style="--sai-vg4guong-bar-h: {{ bar_height }}px; --sai-vg4guong-seg: {{ seg_pct }}%;">
  <script type="application/json" data-sai-progress-config>
{
  "milestones": [
    {%- for m in milestones -%}
    {"threshold": {{ m.thresholdCents | round }}, "title": {{ m.title | json }}, "inactiveHelper": {{ m.inactive.helperText | json }}, "activeHelper": {{ m.active.helperText | json }}, "confetti": {{ m.triggerConfetti | json }}, "confettiAssetUrl": {{ m.active.confettiAssetUrl | json }}, "confettiStyle": {{ m.active.confettiStyle | json }}, "giftVariantId": {{ m.giftVariantId | json }}}{%- unless forloop.last -%},{%- endunless -%}
    {%- endfor -%}
  ],
  "excludedProductIds": {{ cfg.excludedProductIds | json }}
}
  </script>
  <p class="sai-vg4guong__message" data-sai-msg>{{ msg_ssr }}</p>
  <div class="sai-vg4guong__bar" data-sai-bar>
    <div class="sai-vg4guong__track">
      <div class="sai-vg4guong__fill" data-sai-fill style="width: {{ fill_pct }}%;"></div>
    </div>
    {%- for m in milestones -%}
    {%- liquid
      assign pos = forloop.index | times: 100.0 | divided_by: ms_denom
      assign node_t_cents = m.thresholdCents | round
      assign wrap_class = 'sai-vg4guong__node-wrap'
      if cart_total >= node_t_cents
        assign wrap_class = wrap_class | append: ' sai-vg4guong__node-wrap--reached'
      endif
      assign inactive_label = m.inactive.label | default: m.title
      assign active_label = m.active.label | default: m.title
      assign inactive_label_class = 'sai-vg4guong__label'
      if m.inactive.labelPlacement == 'above'
        assign inactive_label_class = inactive_label_class | append: ' sai-vg4guong__label--above'
      endif
      assign active_label_class = 'sai-vg4guong__label'
      if m.active.labelPlacement == 'above'
        assign active_label_class = active_label_class | append: ' sai-vg4guong__label--above'
      endif
    -%}
    <div class="{{ wrap_class }}" data-sai-node data-sai-threshold="{{ node_t_cents }}" data-sai-confetti="{% if m.triggerConfetti %}on{% else %}off{% endif %}" style="left: {{ pos }}%;">
      <div class="sai-vg4guong__state sai-vg4guong__state--inactive">
        {%- case m.inactive.markerStyle -%}
        {%- when 'asset_text' -%}
        <div class="sai-vg4guong__node sai-vg4guong__node--asset">
          {%- if m.inactive.assetUrl -%}<img src="{{ m.inactive.assetUrl }}" alt="" loading="lazy">{%- endif -%}
        </div>
        {%- when 'pin_asset_text' -%}
        <div class="sai-vg4guong__pin">
          {%- if m.inactive.assetUrl -%}<img src="{{ m.inactive.assetUrl }}" alt="" loading="lazy">{%- endif -%}
        </div>
        {%- else -%}
        {%- if m.inactive.assetUrl -%}
        <div class="sai-vg4guong__node sai-vg4guong__node--img"><img src="{{ m.inactive.assetUrl }}" alt="" loading="lazy"></div>
        {%- else -%}
        <div class="sai-vg4guong__node"></div>
        {%- endif -%}
        {%- endcase -%}
        <div class="{{ inactive_label_class }}">{{ inactive_label }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="sai-vg4guong__state sai-vg4guong__state--active">
        {%- case m.active.markerStyle -%}
        {%- when 'asset_text' -%}
        <div class="sai-vg4guong__node sai-vg4guong__node--asset">
          {%- if m.active.assetUrl -%}<img src="{{ m.active.assetUrl }}" alt="" loading="lazy">{%- endif -%}
        </div>
        {%- when 'pin_asset_text' -%}
        <div class="sai-vg4guong__pin">
          {%- if m.active.assetUrl -%}<img src="{{ m.active.assetUrl }}" alt="" loading="lazy">{%- endif -%}
        </div>
        {%- else -%}
        {%- if m.active.assetUrl -%}
        <div class="sai-vg4guong__node sai-vg4guong__node--img"><img src="{{ m.active.assetUrl }}" alt="" loading="lazy"></div>
        {%- else -%}
        <div class="sai-vg4guong__node">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
        </div>
        {%- endif -%}
        {%- endcase -%}
        <div class="{{ active_label_class }}">{{ active_label }}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
  <p class="sai-vg4guong__submsg" data-sai-submsg>{{ submsg_ssr }}</p>
</div>
{%- endif -%}
